title: 02/23/22 DPS Best Of - Rob Parker & Ben Maller Guest Hosting
itunes:title: 02/23/22 DPS Best Of - Rob Parker & Ben Maller Guest Hosting
description:
Rob Parker and Ben Maller, filling in for Dan, debate whether or not Aaron Rodgers is being a drama queen by dragging on the announcement regarding his football future in Green Bay, hand out their letter grades for LeBron James' 4-year run with the Los Angeles Lakers thus far, and discuss why Rob holds daily block parties on Twitter featuring a few of your favorite FOX Sports Radio personalities.
